For example the out parameter in [torch.randn](http://pytorch.org/docs/master/torch.html#torch.randn) is not defined in ATEN randn but it probably uses ATEN randn_out definition. How does that take place? Any pointer would be of great help. (search in the pytorch blog though not thoroughly)
